---
title: Sweet Soy Mushroom Tacos with Creamy Sriracha Slaw & Crispy Fried Onions
description: What are ’shrooms doing in a taco, you ask? Everything, we say! These fabulous funghi are the perfect way to make taco night meatless (and just as satisfying). Creminis are simmered in soy glaze, turning them deliciously sweet and savory. And with the help of some seriously satisfying toppings—tangy sriracha slaw, lime-marinated cucumber, and crispy fried onions—this recipe packs everything you could ever want inside steamy tortillas.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-soy-mushroom-tacos-e2ebe669.jpg
